Maintainer:     Arjun Guha <arjun@cs.brown.edu>
Homepage:       http://www.cs.brown.edu/research/plt/
Stability:      provisional
Category:       Language
Build-Type:     Custom
Synopsis:       JavaScript analysis tools
Description:

	WebBits is a collection of libraries for working with JavaScript.
 
Library
  Hs-Source-Dirs:
    src
  Build-Depends:
    base >= 4 && < 5,
    mtl >= 1.1.0.1,
    parsec < 3.2.0,
    pretty >= 0.1,
    containers >= 0.1,
    syb >= 0.1
  ghc-options:
    -fwarn-incomplete-patterns
  Extensions:    
    DeriveDataTypeable
  Exposed-Modules:
    BrownPLT.JavaScript 
    BrownPLT.JavaScript.Lexer 
    BrownPLT.JavaScript.Parser
    BrownPLT.JavaScript.PrettyPrint
    BrownPLT.JavaScript.Syntax 
    BrownPLT.JavaScript.Environment

Test-Suite test-webbits
  Type: exitcode-stdio-1.0
  Main-Is: Test/Main.hs
  Build-Depends:
    base >= 4 && < 5,
    mtl >= 1.1.0.1,
    parsec < 3.2.0,
    pretty >= 0.1,
    containers >= 0.1,
    syb >= 0.1